statement.p:
For the system of equations given below, determine whether 
each ordered pair is a solution of the system. Type  Yes or  No. 
\begin{array}{rl}
2x-4y \amp  = 4\\
3x+2y \amp  = 6
\end{array}

p.m:
\begin{aligned}
   3x+4y \amp = -8 \\
   3x+4y \mathbf{-3 x} \amp = -8 \mathbf{-3 x} \\ 4 y \amp = -3 x -8 \\
               \frac{4 y}{4} \amp = \frac{-3 x}{4} + \frac{-8}{4} \\
   y \amp = -\left({\frac{3}{4}}\right)x-2
\end{aligned}

statement.p:
